data.description: Welcome to your new home in the quiet Shadow Wood Subdivision in Byron. This 3 bed, 2 bathroom home has recently undergone several updates including LVP flooring, windows, and light fixtures. Tall ceilings in the living area makes the space feel much bigger than it actually is. Sun room offers loads of natural light, overlooking the backyard. Primary bedroom has a walk in closet and an oversized bathroom. Basement is a blank canvas waiting for you to transform into your own, equipped with the potential to create an extra bathroom and has 2 egress windows. Sump pump in basement is newer and the furnace was updated in 2022.  If you are looking for quiet and cozy, this is it!
